───────────────────────────────────────────────
DESCRIPTION

A local-first productivity logging extension for Chrome and Edge.
Tracks work windows every 15 or 30 minutes, auto-detects breaks,
lunch, and overtime. Exports to CSV for weekly manager reporting.

───────────────────────────────────────────────
TECH STACK

Runtime   : Chrome / Edge Extension (MV3)
Storage   : chrome.storage.local (no backend, no cloud)
Scheduler : chrome.alarms API
UI        : Vanilla HTML / CSS / JS

───────────────────────────────────────────────
FILES

  manifest.json   Extension config and permissions
  background.js   Alarm logic, missed/break/overtime tracking
  popup.html      UI — Log, History, Settings tabs
  popup.js        UI logic, CSV export
  icons/          Extension icons (16, 48, 128px)

